title: Cut The Crap Playlist - August 2008
description:
CUT THE CRAP PLAYLIST - August 2008


THIS MONTH: Quite a bit of chillout music, but not all...
also, some British tunes that are on top of the charts over
there but not so much in North America. Apologies to those
who have heard some of these songs over and over again on
the radio =)
`````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````

CTC Monthly Playlists contain 20 of my favourite songs of the
month (not too few, not too many). They aren't necessarily
brand-new songs, but they certainly are worth listening to.
I try to go beyond the mainstream to bring you international
music you may not have heard before, in varying genres.
So, sit back, relax, press play and don't forget to come
back next month for an all-new playlist!

______________________________________________________________

Want more? Check out Mindset for
bite-sized tidbits of interesting things
from around the web and around the world.
Plus, stay updated on the latest CTC Playlists.
